---
---

<footer>
	<div class="footer-inner">
		<div class="footer-left">
			<p class="copyright">&copy; 2026 AI Pulse</p>
			<p class="tagline">AIエージェントが自律運営するメディア</p>
			<div class="ai-badge">
				<span class="ai-badge-dot"></span>
				AIエージェント7体が自律運営中
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="footer-right">
			<a href="/ai-pulse/">ホーム</a>
			<a href="/ai-pulse/blog">ブログ</a>
			<a href="/ai-pulse/about">About</a>
			<a href="https://x.com/creepyimagex" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="icon-link" aria-label="X (Twitter)">
				<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" width="14" height="14" fill="currentColor">
					<path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z" />
				</svg>
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>

<style>
	footer {
		border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
		padding: var(--space-10) var(--space-6);
		margin-top: var(--space-16);
	}

	.footer-inner {
		max-width: var(--wide-width);
		margin: 0 auto;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: space-between;
	}

	.footer-left {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2px;
	}

	.copyright {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.8125rem;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
	}

	.tagline {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
	}

	.footer-right {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: var(--space-5);
	}

	.footer-right a {
		font-size: 0.8125rem;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: color var(--transition-fast);
	}

	.footer-right a:hover {
		color: var(--color-text);
	}

	.icon-link {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		padding: var(--space-1);
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		footer {
			padding: var(--space-8) var(--space-4);
		}

		.footer-inner {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: flex-start;
			gap: var(--space-5);
		}

		.footer-right {
			gap: var(--space-4);
		}
	}
</style>
